(52, 5, 7, 'Medfly Salmon Fish Oil Supplement with Omega 3+6 and Vitamins for Healthy Skin and Coat Pet Health Supplements  (250 ml)', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Omega 3+6 is a concentrated mix of salmon oil, Skin Care aiding vitamins &amp;amp; micro minerals, is a great addition to your pet&#039;s diet. Omega 3+6 play a key role in skin &amp;amp; coat health, decreases allergic intensity &amp;amp; reduces chances of dander &amp;amp; skin scaling. Additional benefits include enhanced brain development, improved immunity, proper cardiac functioning &amp;amp; joint care. Highly palatable &amp;amp; adds good taste to your dog&#039;s food Perfect for dogs of all breeds and ages&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 1, '2024-01-30 12:27:57'),
(53, 5, 7, 'Areion Vet Feli-Lax Hairball Remedy For Cats 50 gm', '&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: karla, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span m&quot;color:#374151;font-family:&#039;s&ouml;hne&#039;,=&quot;&quot; &#039;ui-sans-serif&#039;,=&quot;&quot; &#039;system-ui&#039;,=&quot;&quot; &#039;-apple-system&#039;,=&quot;&quot; &#039;segoe=&quot;&quot; ui&#039;,=&quot;&quot; roboto,=&quot;&quot; ubuntu,=&quot;&quot; cantarell,=&quot;&quot; &#039;noto=&quot;&quot; sans&#039;,=&quot;&quot; sans-serif,=&quot;&quot; &#039;helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue&#039;,=&quot;&quot; arial,=&quot;&quot; &#039;apple=&quot;&quot; color=&quot;&quot; emoji&#039;,=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; symbol&#039;,=&quot;&quot; emoji&#039;;font-size:16px;&quot;=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit;&quot;&gt;Areion Vet Feli-Lax is a product designed for cats to help manage hairballs. It&#039;s a gel-like formulation often given orally to cats to aid in the elimination of ingested hair and to support healthy digestion.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p m&quot;border:0px=&quot;&quot; solid=&quot;&quot; #d9d9e3;margin:1.25em=&quot;&quot; 0px;color:#374151;font-family:&#039;s&ouml;hne&#039;,=&quot;&quot; &#039;ui-sans-serif&#039;,=&quot;&quot; &#039;system-ui&#039;,=&quot;&quot; &#039;-apple-system&#039;,=&quot;&quot; &#039;segoe=&quot;&quot; ui&#039;,=&quot;&quot; roboto,=&quot;&quot; ubuntu,=&quot;&quot; cantarell,=&quot;&quot; &#039;noto=&quot;&quot; sans&#039;,=&quot;&quot; sans-serif,=&quot;&quot; &#039;helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue&#039;,=&quot;&quot; arial,=&quot;&quot; &#039;apple=&quot;&quot; color=&quot;&quot; emoji&#039;,=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; symbol&#039;,=&quot;&quot; emoji&#039;;font-size:16px;&quot;=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: karla, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;The product is generally administered according to the 