(54, 5, 7, 'Sky Ec Fenever Pet Dewormer Oral Suspension 30 ml', '&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: karla, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Introducing Sky Ec Fenever Pet Dewormer Oral Suspension, a reliable and effective solution for your furry companions. This 30 ml bottle contains a broad spectrum deworming suspension specially formulated for kittens and cats.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: karla, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;With its powerful formula, Sky Ec Fenever Pet Dewormer Oral Suspension provides comprehensive protection against a wide range of intestinal parasites. Say goodbye to pesky worms that can harm your pet&#039;s health and vitality.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: karla, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;What sets Sky Ec Fenever Pet Dewormer Oral Suspension apart is its pregnancy-safe formulation. You can rest assured that this product is gentle and safe for use even during your cat&#039;s pregnancy.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: karla, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Ensure the well-being of your beloved feline friend with Sky Ec Fenever Pet Dewormer Oral Suspension. Keep their digestive system healthy and free from harmful parasites. Trust in the power of this broad spectrum deworming suspension to provide the protection your pet deserves.&lt;/p&gt;', 1, '2024-01-30 12:36:53'),
