(72, 1, 3, 'Maxi Persian Fish 14 kg (2x7 kg) Dry Adult Cat Food', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.2px;&quot;&gt;Maxi Persian is a nutrient rich food that has been formulated to deliver a cat&#039;s need for its diet requirement. Enriched with ocean fish and other essential ingredients which helps your feline to maintain the beautiful skin and coat. Taurine, an essential amino acid keeps the heart healthy and promotes the growth and development of the body. We assure all our ingredients goes through a strict selection process by nutritional laboratories to meet the safety and quality standards of the product. Our extensive research guarantees high palatability, better digestibility.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 1, '2024-02-03 05:05:40'),
(73, 1, 3, 'Drools Real Chicken Cat Treat  (400 g)', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Drools Cat Biscuit is made of good quality ingredients such as real chicken, egg, rice flour and wheat flour. Each biscuit offers complete nutrition with no added artificial flavours and colours. The cat biscuits are crunchy and crispy, and can be used as treats for your cat whenever you want to reward them. It helps in slowing down the tartar buildup, the optimal proportion of omega 3 and 6 fatty acids helps the cats to maintain a healthy and lustrous coat.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 1, '2024-02-03 05:07:48'),
(74, 1, 3, 'Wiggles Kittystix Cat Treats for Kittens Kitty Soft', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Curated by vets for your pets - Protein with immunity-boosting herbs, Rich in taurine and arginine, Bite-sized and No artificial enhancers Packed With Health Benefits - Builds strong joints, Promotes healthy skin and coat, Boosts digestion and immunity and Improves eyesight and heart health Daily Feeding Guidelines - Kittens above 2 months of age (Upto 1-2 kg) - 2 to 3 pcs, Small-Sized Cats (Upto 3-4 kg) - 5 to 6 pcs, Medium-Sized Cats (Upto 4-5 kg) - 7 to 10 pcs &amp;amp; Large-Sized Cats (More than 6 kg) - 11 to 13 pcs Give Treats To Your Kitty - After using the litter box/cat scratcher, After feeding medicines, As a positive reinforcement when your cat follows basic commands and leash training Storage and usage - Store in a cool and dry place, away from direct sunlight. Refrigerate in an air-tight container after opening to ensure maximum safety. Make sure the seal is intact before buying. Once opened, consume within 10 to 12 days. Contains moisture-absorbent sachet&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', 1, '2024-02-03 05:13:17'),
(75, 1, 1, 'purepet Mutton Flavour Real Biscuit ', '&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Purepet Dog Biscuits are nutritious dog treats which gives immense joy to your pet. They are made with Real Chicken, our #1 ingredient, with no added artificial colors or flavors. It helps to maintain clean teeth and also freshen breath by controlling the tartar build up, and promotes lustrous and healthy coat.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;', 1, '2024-02-03 05:17:41'),
